.SH QEMU VIRTUAL MACHINES
desktopmgr provides integrated QEMU virtual machine management through Docker containers:
.TP
.B qemu linux
Launch AlmaLinux 9 VM with web interface on port 65301
.TP
.B qemu windows
Launch Windows VM with web interface on port 65302
.TP
.B qemu macos
Launch macOS Ventura VM with web interface on port 65303
.TP
.B qemu arm
Launch ARM64 Alpine Linux VM with web interface on port 65304
.PP
All VMs are configured with:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
4GB RAM
.IP \(bu 2
100GB disk space
.IP \(bu 2
2 CPU cores
.IP \(bu 2
Web-based VNC access
.IP \(bu 2
Persistent storage in ~/.local/share/qemu/<vm-name>/
.RE
