.SH NOTES
.IP \(bu 2
Desktop environment installations are managed through preconfigured GitHub repositories under the desktopmgr organization
.IP \(bu 2
Each desktop environment package includes configuration files, themes, and necessary setup scripts
.IP \(bu 2
QEMU virtual machines require /dev/kvm to be accessible and virtualization to be enabled in BIOS
.IP \(bu 2
VM containers use significant resources (4GB RAM per VM)
.IP \(bu 2
Installed configurations are tracked in ~/.local/share/CasjaysDev/apps/desktopmgr/
.IP \(bu 2
Desktop notifications can be disabled by setting DESKTOPMGR_NOTIFY_ENABLED=no
